reviewText: Excellent. A must see. Also one on Mexico as well. I hope he does more Royal Tours
The President was the tour guide to this beautiful country. His pride and love for his people was real and did not seem forced like most politicians. Excellent documentary.
The President of Ecuador showcases his country; he is a real ham, champion of his country, leader of the people and entertainer.
Very educational and provides enough information to make you visit such a beautiful country.
Now Ecuador is on my travel bucket list!
It was great seeing the various areas of Ecuador through the eyes of the president!  He makes a great spokesman for his country.
Very well done documentary and portrait of Ecuador attractions.... with the president as a bonus...
There is so much more in Ecuador to explore. The highlights that were hit in this movie were great and they added a bit of background to make it more personable and inviting.

Absolutely enjoyed this video, make me want to visit.  A President who has not forgotten where he came from, is very proud of his country and people and knows his country inside out.  He is very humble and  charismatic, and made the tour extremely enjoyable.  I have to watch it one more time.  He has my blessings.
My high school aged Spanish students found this very interesting.

I have friends from Ecuador.  This is a fascinating presentation of their beautiful country from their presidente - no kidding.  Makes me want to travel there.  Though I don't think that I'll be lucky enough to have the presidente tag along.
Can't wait to retire in Ecuador !!!
A wonderful documentary! An small country, the size of Colorado. It has beautiful places. I want to go to see it!
